t: 0.6833em;"></span><span class=3D"mord mathnormal">A</span><span class=3D=
"mspace" style=3D"margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class=3D"mrel">=3D<=
/span><span class=3D"mspace" style=3D"margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></spa=
n><span class=3D"base"><span class=3D"strut" style=3D"height: 0.6667em; ver=
